Package: fidelitysim
Title: Fidelity patterns in simulation experiments for cluster randomized trials in implementation science research
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Diana", "Trutschel", , "diana@trutschel.de", role = c("aut"),
            comment =c(ORCID = "")),
    person("Catherine", "Blatter", , "catherine.blatter@unibas.ch", role = c("ctb", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4069-7178")))
Description: The package provides functions to coduct simulation experiments for 
  investigating the performance of effect estimation within parallel/stepped-wedged 
  cluster randomized trials under consideration of implementation error (measured by fidelity).
